      </video>
     </span>
     <h2 class="bb_tag">
      <strong>
       FEATURES
      </strong>
     </h2>
     <ul class="bb_ul">
      <li>
       Explore the tactical depth of this explosive gameplay blend between tank simulation and tactical real-time strategy
       <br/>
      </li>
      <li>
       Manage your tank by utilizing the chain of command and achieve victory in tactical combat by clever management of supporting infantry and armored units in a dynamic battle spаcе
       <br/>
