<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph" style="text-align: center">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="138" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/7e4358f918cef8fe7c43fa080cc699bd.poster.avif?t=1773514901" width="700">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/7e4358f918cef8fe7c43fa080cc699bd.webm?t=1773514901" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/7e4358f918cef8fe7c43fa080cc699bd.mp4?t=1773514901" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   Funi Raccoon Game
  </strong>
  , a 3D Platformer Collectathon. You play as a raccoon who has recently acquired a new home (Dumpster).
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="480" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/c16ada8c79a880e845e7ed5f5b3b4e44.poster.avif?t=1773514901" width="640">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/c16ada8c79a880e845e7ed5f5b3b4e44.webm?t=1773514901" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/c16ada8c79a880e845e7ed5f5b3b4e44.mp4?t=1773514901" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Home is where the stuff is, but your home is pretty empty. Fill up your dumpster with cool, unique stuff. The more stuff you have, the more places you can go! Travel the lands, "help" the locals, and solve puzzles --
  <i>
   <strong>
    all in the aim to get more stuff!?!
   </strong>
  </i>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag" style="text-align: center">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="112" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/153e544df3ee55c98fd84f8df47f154b.poster.avif?t=1773514901" width="400">
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/153e544df3ee55c98fd84f8df47f154b.webm?t=1773514901" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3599690/extras/153e544df3ee55c98fd84f8df47f154b.mp4?t=1773514901" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </h2>
